Sentencas: The anode-supported single cell was constructed with porous Ni-Yittria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) as the anode substrate, an airtight YSZ as the electrolyte, and a screen-printed La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-delta (LSM)-Gadolinia-doped ceria (GDC)/LSM double-layer cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of the electrochemical performance of the anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with the composite cathode of La0.8Sr0.2Mn3-δ-Gadolinia-doped ceria oxide/La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ

Sentencas: The SEM results show that the YSZ thin film is highly integrated, fully dense with a thickness of 13 mu m, and exhibits excellent compatibility between cathode and electrolyte layers.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of the electrochemical performance of the anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with the composite cathode of La0.8Sr0.2Mn3-δ-Gadolinia-doped ceria oxide/La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ

Sentencas: The effects of feed rates of the reactants, temperature, and contact pressure between the current collector and the unit cell were systematically investigated.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of the electrochemical performance of the anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with the composite cathode of La0.8Sr0.2Mn3-δ-Gadolinia-doped ceria oxide/La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ

Sentencas: The results are based on the assumption that the anode contribution to the polarization resistance is negligible.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of the electrochemical performance of the anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with the composite cathode of La0.8Sr0.2Mn3-δ-Gadolinia-doped ceria oxide/La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-δ

Sentencas: Our analysis showed that the electrochemical reaction is limited by mass transfer control when the airflow rate is decreased to 500 ml min(-1).
